Modifications
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

SpecOps is a derivative work of Clawforce. Files carried over from Clawforce
have been modified from their original form. Notable project-wide changes
include, but are not limited to:

  * Rebrand from Clawforce / Clawbot / clawlib to SpecOps / SpecialAgent /
    specops_lib (Python distributions, imports, CLI commands, environment
    variable prefixes, Docker images, UI routes, components, and hooks).
  * Addition of plan templates, human-review gates on plan tasks, a user
    dashboard, dark mode, CI pipeline, and reverse-proxy deployment docs.

A more complete, commit-level history of modifications is available in
CHANGELOG.md and in the project's git log.
